# mam-playground

Playing around with how to architect a text based adventure like
https://github.com/buntine/Medieval-Alien-Massacre

## Goal

- Try to move north
  - "This door needs a key"
- Speak to person
  - "I'll trade you a candle for a key"
- Pick up candle
- Trade candle for key
- Speak to person
  - "Candles make great dildos"
- Move north
  - "Your key unlocked the door"

